  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"minus 2 x squared plus 20 x plus c equals 0\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t<mo>-</mo>\n\t\t\t<mn>2</mn>\n\t\t\t<msup>\n\t\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t\t\t<mn>2</mn>\n\t\t\t</msup>\n\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t<mn>20</mn>\n\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t\t<mi>c</mi>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mn>0</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In the given equation, <math alttext=\"c\"><mi>c</mi>\n</math> is a constant. The equation has exactly one solution. What is the value of <math alttext=\"c\"><mi>c</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
